Anda masih hidup! Awak dah bangun!

163
00:14:54,387 --> 00:14:55,638
Saya tidak percaya itu.

164
00:14:57,473 --> 00:14:59,142
Ada apa dengan reaksi berlebihan?

165
00:15:00,685 --> 00:15:03,688
Tunggu, saya tidak boleh bernafas.
Awak boleh lepaskan saya sekarang.

166
00:15:04,564 --> 00:15:06,024
Saya mungkin benar-benar mati.

167
00:15:06,065 --> 00:15:08,526
Maaf, saya sangat gembira.

168
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,612
Tetapi, apa...

169
00:15:11,613 --> 00:15:12,780
Duduklah.

170
00:15:13,656 --> 00:15:17,367
Adakah anda lapar? dahaga? Apa yang anda perlukan?

171
00:15:17,368 --> 00:15:19,495
- Jururawat! Jururawat...
- Okay.

172
00:15:19,704 --> 00:15:21,331
Lorelei, saya okay.

173
00:15:22,165 --> 00:15:23,165
Okay.

174
00:15:26,210 --> 00:15:27,378
Adakah anda berasa pening?

175
00:15:31,758 --> 00:15:33,134
Jangan tekankan diri anda.

176
00:15:36,387 --> 00:15:37,388
Perlahan-lahan.

177
00:15:41,225 --> 00:15:42,225
Tunggu.

178
00:15:42,769 --> 00:15:44,062
Bagaimana saya boleh sampai ke sini?

179
00:15:46,189 --> 00:15:49,484
jangan beritahu saya
awak bawa saya ke sini dari kampus?

180
00:15:50,485 --> 00:15:53,613
Saya mungkin telah membawa awak sendiri
jika saya tidak mendapat bantuan.

181
00:15:54,697 --> 00:15:56,532
Loki, bangun!

182
00:15:56,824 --> 00:15:59,452
Tolong. Tolong!

183
00:16:00,954 --> 00:16:02,246
Tolong!

184
00:16:03,665 --> 00:16:05,583
- Loki tidak sedarkan diri.
- Loki!

185
00:16:06,209 --> 00:16:08,044
Loki! Loki!

186
00:16:10,463 --> 00:16:11,631
Tolong!

187
00:16:12,298 --> 00:16:13,675
Dapatkan bantuan di sini!

188
00:16:14,592 --> 00:16:15,592
Tolong.

189
00:16:20,974 --> 00:16:25,061
Perkara yang baik Profesor Morayta
berada berhampiran bilik kelab

190
00:16:25,353 --> 00:16:27,605
dan segera meminta pertolongan,

191
00:16:27,939 --> 00:16:30,233
untuk membawa awak ke sini di hospital.

192
00:16:33,069 --> 00:16:35,321
Prof... Profesor Morayta?

193
00:16:36,197 --> 00:16:39,367
Ya, profesor Matematik 100 saya.

194
00:16:40,076 --> 00:16:42,745
Dan pelanggan kami dalam kes Stein Alberts.

195
00:16:43,454 --> 00:16:44,454
Ingat?

196
00:16:44,831 --> 00:16:46,708
Ya. Saya ingat sekarang.

197
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:51,087
Maaf, fikiran saya masih berjerebu.

198
00:16:51,337 --> 00:16:52,337
